  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Demographic information and a brief medical and concomitant medicine history will be obtained
      from the glaucoma patient's records. Qualified patients will be asked to complete a
      questionnaire about their symptoms. Patients will then be scheduled to undergo three standard
      clinical tests of the ocular surface.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
